epgy stanford university education program for gifted youth school open enrollment picture sign in to your epgy account user id password home what is school open enrollment courses tuition support frequently asked questions contact us sign up tuition students have the option of enrolling for either a 10 month or a 5 month enrollment period both options include k 7 mathematics language arts and writing and beginning algebra 10 month enrollment $135 5 month enrollment $95 activation fee $25 there is a $25 activation fee for new students the activation fee also applies to students whose courses have expired enrolled students can add another 10 month or 5 month period at any time before the courses expire by using the re enrollment tool located on the student page once the courses expire the activation fee will apply refunds requests for refunds must be received in writing within 21 days of enrollment no refunds will be issued thereafter the $25 activation fee is non refundable stanford university epgy 2008
